/*
   Flappy Bird Game

   This program implements a simplified version of Flappy Bird using an STM32
   microcontroller. Control the bird with the "Up" button, navigate through
   moving pipes, and increase your score. The game ends if the bird collides
   with the ground or pipes.

   Components: STM32, graphical display

   How to Play:
   1. On the title screen, press "Up" or "Down" to start.
   2. Control the bird's upward movement with the "Up" button.
   3. Navigate through pipes to increase your score.
   4. Collisions end the game; final score is displayed.

   Game Loop: Updates bird, pipes, and checks collisions. Adjust speed with
   delay parameter.

   Developed by Sean Cleary(C22512873)
   Module : Microprocessors 
   Date: 23/11/23

*/


